additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Apple Cider Vinegar Powder (Apple Cider Vinegar Solids, Maltodextrin) (87%), Bulking Agent (Calcium Phosphate), Glazing Agents (Polyethylene Glycol, Carnauba Wax), Anticaking Agents (Silicon Dioxide, Magnesium Stearate).

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Do not use if cap seal is broken.

description: Swisse High Strength Apple Cider Vinegar with 'The Mother' is a premium quality formula containing Australian-sourced apple cider vinegar. The convenient tablet format is 98% fat free and enables you to enjoy all the benefits of apple cider vinegar without the strong taste and smell.
name: High Strength Australian Apple Cider Vinegar
